12.4 Industrial action
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You cannot use your Dankort card in Denmark if &BANKNAVN. and/or
&BANKNAVN.'s data centres become involved in industrial action. On the
commencement or termination of such a conflict, you will be informed
of same without undue delay through advertisements in the daily
newspapers and via other channels.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
