13¤Expiry
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
You can use the card up to and including the month of expiry stated on
the card, after which it will become invalid. Dankort card on mobile phone
expires at the same time as the card to which it is connected.
.sp 3mm
Before the card expires, a new card will be sent to you, or you will be
informed that a new card is ready for you to collect from
&BANKNAVN.. When receiving a new card, you must connect your Dankort card
to the mobile phone again.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
14¤Termination
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
&BANKNAVN. may terminate the agreement on two months' notice. In the
event of termination, you will receive a refund of a proportional
amount of any fees you may have paid in advance for the use of the card.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You can terminate the agreement with &BANKNAVN. on one month's notice.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If you terminate the agreement within six months, &BANKNAVN. may charge
a fee for termination of the agreement, see the &BANKNAVN. price list.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If you or &BANKNAVN. choose to terminate the agreement, you must
return the card to &BANKNAVN.. If you return the card by mail, you
must cut the card into pieces before returning it.
.sp 5mm
